/h1><p class=\"mt-4 text-muted-foreground\">Have a question, suggestion, or found a bug? We&#x27;d love to hear from you. Reach out at<!-- --> <a href=\"mailto:hello@freetoolshed.com\" class=\"text-brand underline underline-offset-4\">hello@freetoolshed.com</a> <!-- -->and we&#x27;ll get back to you as soon as we can.</p><div data-orientation=\"horizontal\" role=\"separator\" aria-orientation=\"horizontal\" data-slot=\"separator\" class=\"shrink-0 bg-border data-horizontal:h-px data-horizontal:w-full data-vertical:w-px data-vertical:self-stretch my-8\"></div><h2 class=\"text-xl font-semibold\">How Can We Help?</h2><div class=\"mt-4 grid gap-4 sm:grid-cols-2\"><div data-slot=\"card\" data-size=\"default\" class=\"group/card flex-col overflow-hidden rounded-xl bg-card text-sm text-card-foreground ring-1 ring-foreground/10 has-data-[slot=card-footer]:pb-0 has-[&gt;img:first-child]:pt-0 data-[size=sm]:gap-3 data-[size=sm]:py-3 data-[size=sm]:has-data-[slot=card-footer]:pb-0 *:[img:first-child]:rounded-t-xl *:[img:last-child]:rounded-b-xl flex gap-3 p-4\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-bug mt-0.5 size-5 shrink-0 text-brand\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M12 20v-9\"></path><path d=\"M14 7a4 4 0 0 1 4 4v3a6 6 0 0 1-12 0v-3a4 4 0 0 1 4-4z\"></path><path d=\"M14.12 3.88 16 2\"></path><path d=\"M21 21a4 4 0 0 0-3.81-4\"></path><path d=\"M21 5a4 4 0 0 1-3.55 3.97\"></path><path d=\"M22 13h-4\"></path><path d=\"M3 21a4 4 0 0 1 3.81-4\"></path><path d=\"M3 5a4 4 0 0 0 3.55 3.97\"></path><path d=\"M6 13H2\"></path><path d=\"m8 2 1.88 1.88\"></path><path d=\"M9 7.13V6a3 3 0 1 1 6 0v1.13\"></path></svg><div><h3 class=\"text-sm font-semibold\">Report a Bug</h3><p class=\"mt-1 text-sm text-muted-foreground\">Something not working right? Let us know which tool, what you expected to happen, and what happened instead. Screenshots help.</p></div></div><div data-slot=\"card\" data-size=\"default\" class=\"group/card flex-col overflow-hidden rounded-xl bg-card text-sm text-card-foreground ring-1 ring-foreground/10 has-data-[slot=card-footer]:pb-0 has-[&gt;img:first-child]:pt-0 data-[size=sm]:gap-3 data-[size=sm]:py-3 data-[size=sm]:has-data-[slot=card-footer]:pb-0 *:[img:first-child]:rounded-t-xl *:[img:last-child]:rounded-b-xl flex gap-3 p-4\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-lightbulb mt-0.5 size-5 shrink-0 text-brand\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M15 14c.2-1 .7-1.7 1.5-2.5 1-.9 1.5-2.2 1.5-3.5A6 6 0 0 0 6 8c0 1 .2 2.2 1.5 3.5.7.7 1.3 1.5 1.5 2.5\"></path><path d=\"M9 18h6\"></path><path d=\"M10 22h4\"></path></svg><div><h3 class=\"text-sm font-semibold\">Suggest a Tool</h3><p class=\"mt-1 text-sm text-muted-foreground\">Is there a paid tool you wish was free? Tell us what it does and why you need it — the most requested tools get built first.</p></div></div><div data-slot=\"card\" data-size=\"default\" class=\"group/card flex-col overflow-hidden rounded-xl bg-card text-sm text-card-foreground ring-1 ring-foreground/10 has-data-[slot=card-footer]:pb-0 has-[&gt;img:first-child]:pt-0 data-[size=sm]:gap-3 data-[size=sm]:py-3 data-[size=sm]:has-data-[slot=card-footer]:pb-0 *:[img:first-child]:rounded-t-xl *:[img:last-child]:rounded-b-xl flex gap-3 p-4\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-circle-question-mark mt-0.5 size-5 shrink-0 text-brand\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"10\"></circle><path d=\"M9.09 9a3 3 0 0 1 5.83 1c0 2-3 3-3 3\"></path><path d=\"M12 17h.01\"></path></svg><div><h3 class=\"text-sm font-semibold\">General Questions</h3><p class=\"mt-1 text-sm text-muted-foreground\">Questions about how the site works, our privacy practices, or anything else? We&#x27;re happy to answer.</p></div></div><div data-slot=\"card\" data-size=\"default\" class=\"group/card flex-col overflow-hidden rounded-xl bg-card text-sm text-card-foreground ring-1 ring-foreground/10 has-data-[slot=card-footer]:pb-0 has-[&gt;img:first-child]:pt-0 data-[size=sm]:gap-3 data-[size=sm]:py-3 data-[size=sm]:has-data-[slot=card-footer]:pb-0 *:[img:first-child]:rounded-t-xl *:[img:last-child]:rounded-b-xl flex gap-3 p-4\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-mail mt-0.5 size-5 shrink-0 text-brand\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"m22 7-8.991 5.727a2 2 0 0 1-2.009 0L2 7\"></path><rect x=\"2\" y=\"4\" width=\"20\" height=\"16\" rx=\"2\"></rect></svg><div><h3 class=\"text-sm font-semibold\">Business Inquiries</h3><p class=\"mt-1 text-sm text-muted-foreground\">Partnership opportunities, advertising questions, or press inquiries — reach out and we&#x27;ll point you in the right direction.</p></div></div></div><div data-orientation=\"horizontal\" role=\"separator\" aria-orientation=\"horizontal\" data-slot=\"separator\" class=\"shrink-0 bg-border data-horizontal:h-px data-horizontal:w-full data-vertical:w-px data-vertical:self-stretch my-8\"></div><section><h2 class=\"text-xl font-semibold\">Frequently Asked</h2><div class=\"mt-4 space-y-4\"><div><h3 class=\"text-sm font-semibold\">What&#x27;s the typical response time?</h3><p class=\"mt-1 text-sm text-muted-foreground\">We aim to respond within 1–2 business days. Bug reports for broken tools are prioritized.</p></div><div><h3 class=\"text-sm font-semibold\">Is there a community or forum?</h3><p class=\"mt-1 text-sm text-muted-foreground\">Not yet, but it&#x27;s on our radar. For now, email is the best way to reach us.</p></div><div><h3 class=\"text-sm font-semibold\">I found a security issue. How do I report it?</h3><p class=\"mt-1 text-sm text-muted-foreground\">Please email us directly at<!-- --> <a href=\"mailto:hello@freetoolshed.com\" class=\"text-brand underline underline-offset-4\">hello@freetoolshed.com</a> <!-- -->with &quot;Security&quot; in the subject line. We take these reports seriously and will respond promptly.</p></div></div></section></main><!--$--><!--/$--></div><footer class=\"border-t border-border bg-muted/40\"><div class=\"mx-auto flex max-w-7xl flex-col items-center gap-4 px-4 py-8 sm:flex-row sm:justify-between sm:px-6 lg:px-8\"><p class=\"text-sm text-muted-foreground\">© <!-- -->2026<!-- --> Free Tool Shed. All rights reserved.</p><nav class=\"flex gap-4 text-sm text-muted-foreground\"><a class=\"transition-colors hover:text-foreground\" href=\"/about\">About</a><a class=\"transition-colors hover:text-foreground\" href=\"/contact\">Contact</a><a class=\"transition-colors hover:text-foreground\" href=\"/privacy\">Privacy</a><a class=\"transition-colors hover:text-foreground\" href=\"/terms\">Terms</a></nav></div></footer><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/0eyplc079uusk.js\" id=\"_R_\" async=\"\"></script><script>(self.__next_f=self.__next_f||[]).push([0])</script><script>self.__next_f.push([1,\"1:\\\"$Sreact.fragment\\\"\\n2:I[83661,[\\\"/_next/static/chunks/0zif8_3mgcc0x.js\\\",\\\"/_next/static/chunks/0zv.me6xdrdsz.js\\\",\\\"/_next/static/chunks/0ag6f0zogt0qg.js\\\",\\\"/_next/static/chunks/04p0ygcx_g620.js\\\",\\\"/_next/static/chunks/0d3shmwh5_nmn.js\\\",\\\"/_next/static/chunks/0_pa1c_tsbiw0.js\\\",\\\"/_next/static/chunks/10nuyoal1pib2.js\\\"],\\\"ThemeProvider\\\"]\\n3:I[46798,[\\\"/_next/static/chunks/0zif8_3mgcc0x.js\\\",\\\"/_next/static/chunks/0zv.me6xdrdsz.js\\\",\\\"/_next/static/chunks/0ag6f0zogt0qg.js\\\",\\\"/_next/static/chunks/04p0ygcx_g620.js\\\",\\\